TransCo tender for Sept , Oct gas closes . British Gas Plc pipeline arm TransCo confirmed on Tuesday that a tender for gas for September and October closed this afternoon . TransCo tendered for 3 , 759 gigaWatt hours to be injected into storage during September and October , a spokesman said . This equates to around 2 . 10 million therms a day if delivered evenly over the two months . TransCo will notify successful tenderers on Thursday . The gas is for " operating and balancing margins " - - in effect storage cover for the winter . - - London Newsroom + 44 171 542 6412 
